                            <comment id="13051838" author="vivekp" created="Mon, 20 Jun 2011 08:53:25 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Attaching an initial patch&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13051841" author="vivekp" created="Mon, 20 Jun 2011 09:02:11 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Please note that , if compression is used, then the subfolders and output files will be having the corresponding extension.&lt;br/&gt;
For example, if output001.bz2 is output path and f1,f2 are the keys, the files will look like;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;/tmp/output001.bz2 &lt;br/&gt;
   /tmp/output001.bz2/f1.bz2&lt;br/&gt;
